data.description: Inspiring mountain & valley views! Beautifully designed 1,935 SqFt single level 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with flowing floor plan + 3 car attached garage situated on 16. 37 acres. Spacious living room perfect for gatherings featuring a wood burning fireplace & soaring vaulted ceilings. Open concept kitchen w/granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & generous sized chef island with additional seating that opens to the dinette area & a separate formal dining room. Primary suite features a large picture window w/ a jaw dropping views, en suite w/ jetted tub, walk-in closet & dual vanity.  Step outside to enjoy the outdoors -established orchard (apple, peach, cherry trees), spacious yard area, 2 sheds & producing irrigated hay ground.
